{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmailTags:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSDictionary","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"tags","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"forEmail:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"email","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"completion:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"tags","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to associate with the email."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"email","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The email address to associate tags with."}]}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Same as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setEmailTags:forEmail:"},{"text":" but provides confirmation when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Use this when you need to verify tags were set before proceeding with other operations.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Verify email and update tags with confirmation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class EmailVerificationService {","","    func completeEmailVerification(email: String, verificationCode: String,","                                   completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.verifyEmail(email, code: verificationCode) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success:","                let verificationTags: [String: Any] = [","                    \"email_verified\": true,","                    \"verification_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                    \"verification_method\": \"code\"","                ]","","                Pushwoosh.configure.setEmailTags(verificationTags, forEmail: email) { error in","                    if let error = error {","                        Logger.warning(\"Email tags update failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                        \/\/ Continue anyway - email is verified on backend","                    }","","                    \/\/ Also update device tags","                    Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([\"has_verified_email\": true])","","                    completion(.success(()))","                }","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmailTags:forEmail:completion:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setEmailTags:forEmail:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":